As we are planning to host a python web application, we are using flask which is a python web framework which is used to create python web applications.

# SG configuration
In your EC2 security configuration make sure port 80 is opened.

# Create a ec2 instance linux OS and switch as root user
sudo su

# Install python
python —version
yum install python — 3.9.16

# Install pip
yum install pip -y
pip -V

# Install flask
pip install flask
python -c "import flask; print(flask.__version__)"

# Install virtual environment and activate the same
pip install virtualenv
virtualenv venv
source ./venv/bin/activate
